Sentencas: A novel anode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with a composite of LaxSr1-xTiO3 has been synthesized by a sol-gel auto-combustion method.
Titulo: SYNTHESIS OF LAXSR1-XTIO3 ANODE MATERIALS BY SOL-GEL AUTO-COMBUSTION METHOD

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction (XRD) shows that LaxSr(1-x)TiO(3) has good chemical compatibility with Gd0.2Ce0.8O1 9 electrolyte.
Titulo: SYNTHESIS OF LAXSR1-XTIO3 ANODE MATERIALS BY SOL-GEL AUTO-COMBUSTION METHOD

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) of the as-prepared anode material is similar to that of Gd0.2Ce0.8O19.
Titulo: SYNTHESIS OF LAXSR1-XTIO3 ANODE MATERIALS BY SOL-GEL AUTO-COMBUSTION METHOD

Sentencas: The electric conductivity measurements show that the conductivity of LaxSr1-xTiO3 increases with the increasing of lanthanum contents and reached a maximal value at x=0.3.
Titulo: SYNTHESIS OF LAXSR1-XTIO3 ANODE MATERIALS BY SOL-GEL AUTO-COMBUSTION METHOD

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C, the electrical conductivity of La0.3Sr0.7TiO3 is 184S.cm(-1).
Titulo: SYNTHESIS OF LAXSR1-XTIO3 ANODE MATERIALS BY SOL-GEL AUTO-COMBUSTION METHOD
